              <span id="reviewTextContainer1473796742" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15025346587729358878">Such a ridiculously beautiful magical realism YA about the process of claiming your gender and identity, your body, your name, and how to best support and love someone in that process. For so many reasons - the writing, the PoC (Latina and South Asian) representation, the trans representation, the on-page sex - I am so excited this book is in the world. </span>

          </span>
